# Architecture Skill

## Objective
Design and maintain a scalable, maintainable mobile-first application architecture.

## Responsibilities
- Define application layers
- Enforce separation of concerns
- Maintain modular structure
- Prevent tightly coupled components
- Ensure scalability for future features

## Architecture Pattern
Follow Clean Architecture:

1. Presentation Layer
   - UI Components
   - Screens
   - Navigation

2. Application Layer
   - Controllers
   - State Management
   - Business workflows

3. Domain Layer
   - Business logic
   - Entities
   - Use cases

4. Infrastructure Layer
   - APIs
   - Database
   - External integrations

## Rules
- UI must never call APIs directly
- Business logic must remain reusable
- Each feature must exist as an independent module
- Avoid global dependencies

## Folder Strategy
/features
/shared
/services
/core
